website_summaries.verdict: Will last for the life of your car, but may not interest you if you don't like the camo design.
pros: Several designs and colors available and easy to trim
Raised edges trap liquids so they won't spill onto floor of car
cons: Comes with only 2 mats per pack
All the designs have to do with camo or hunting

customer_reviews.title: Beautiful! Very detailed!
customer_reviews.text: I am so very happy with these floor mats! I gifted them to my husband and he loves them in his truck! The design of them is amazing. I've never found this look in stores. They came super fast! I love the detail in them, the deer head is beautiful in the middle and the quality of the camo and the colors are amazing! If your looking for camo floor mats look no further because these are the best!
customer_reviews.author: JoAnna Marcum

customer_reviews.title: Strong chemical odor
customer_reviews.text: Mats seem heavy duty, however the chemical odor (rubber off-gassing) make the mats unusable. The entire interior of the vehicle smelled of chemicals for 2 days after removing the mats! Not to mention, breathing rubber off-gas is usually unsafe. I've had them out in the sun for 2 weeks now, but the chemical odor still remains. The odd thing is that the rear mats (sold separately) aren't nearly as bad. Having the rears in the sun for a few days removed the odor. Unfortunately, the front mats seem to be made of a different type of rubber (looks slightly different).
customer_reviews.author: SVTHOMAS

customer_reviews.title: Great item
customer_reviews.text: I bought these as a gift for my dad. He loves them! They are extremely heavy duty and they have a slight raised border that keeps water in the matt so it can be dumped instead of running underneath. The design is also very nice.
customer_reviews.author: Bonnie J. Kelly
